input.activity_signal: Multiple sources indicate inactive status: CorporationWiki states "The company was incorporated in California twenty-eight years ago and is no longer active." Aelea Christofferson's own website states "Prior to my retirement, I owned ATL Communications" suggesting she has retired from the business. Only one FCC filing from 2016 with no recent activity. Web search shows speaking engagements from 2015 but no current business operations.
input.product_summary: ATL Communications was a telecommunications company specializing in managing and routing toll-free numbers, serving clients worldwide from its founding in 1993 until closure.
